Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:12.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個城裡的人都是糞土
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:17.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:19.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要斬草除根
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:24.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,殺光這個城裡的所有士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:03.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,檔案和地圖之類的 全部都不要放過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:06.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕是稍微潦草一點的筆記也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:09.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1701.6,117)}第六幕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:09.62,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1411.2,241.8)}MEN OF DESTINY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:08.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都要一併帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:16.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:19.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然真的把城給攻陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:23.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 奧爾米·乳 你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:26.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經連對你吐槽的精力都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:29.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在放棄的話 戰爭就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:37.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 喂 這是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:39.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是好大的一幅畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:43.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是這個國家——奧爾特的國父
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,創造奧爾特帝國的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:49.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在六十年前突然出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道漂流者還是廢棄物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,詳細的事情我們也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:59.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,某天他在酒館出現並煽動群眾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:03.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,憑藉著他天才般的演講技能和人心掌握術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:06.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,掀起了起義的大旗並向首都進發
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,根據按照當時的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:11.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「他似乎已經很熟練了」 這樣記載的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:16.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後 奧爾特建國後就好像突然自殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:19.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原因到現在為止也被謎團所重重包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:25.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是漂流者的話會認識這個人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:26.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:29.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個鬍鬚是怎麼回事 是在瞧不起人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:30.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,豐久先生把敵兵拽到庭院裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要把他們給斬草 除根了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:40.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什…麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:43.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:47.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,豐啊 你無論到那裡都是那麼地正直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 「除根」是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是全部殺光的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:53.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:56.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看到精靈族的男人以後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,應該也能斷定精靈族的女人都是美女了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:02.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,既然定期地把她們給擄走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵肯定會侵犯她們的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:08.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情 在城堡攻陷之前不是應該都懂的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:13.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,斬草除根什麼的 你可不能做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:17.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,打從一開始 幹那些髒活可都是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就保持著那份正直活下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:25.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,邪門歪道就交給我這個第六天魔王就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 我可是很熟練的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:38.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,饒…饒命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,求你放過我們一條生路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們知道這樣會有什麼下場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:56.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們讓本國知道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,保證會讓你們全死光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:04:59.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,豐久先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們放箭吧 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:05.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們殺掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,豐久先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,殺…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:24.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,殺掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:26.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把他們殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:31.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前為止 你們可是盡情地玩弄了這些女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:34.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想著僅僅是扔棄武器表示投降就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:36.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這可就是大錯特錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:41.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些傢伙 不是一心想把他們給滅絕的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:45.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就算反被消滅也算是天經地義的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:48.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧 死了之後變成火藥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄準
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:56.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:59.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明明到目前為止把我們剝削得這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:02.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在輪到你們的時候卻來求饒麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:05.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是剛剛被派遣過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都…什麼都沒做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:11.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已經能夠起來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:32.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是用盡全力打下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:34.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,薩州人還真是健壯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵我都已經給處理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是個不錯的光景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼下這種命令還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:50.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我的手早已抹黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:54.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,伊勢長島
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:55.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK}比叡山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:55.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,延曆寺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:57.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,淺井朝倉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,數不盡數
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,數…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:06.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情 我才不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情 與我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:16.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 怎麼了 是在打架麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,並非打架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:25.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是啊 不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:32.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被人揍完之後訓斥什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:33.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是令人懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,自從父親大人以後還沒有過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:39.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像還把平手那老頭給惹怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:39.66,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,7.8)}註：平手政秀，戰國時代的武將。織田信長之子織田信秀的老師。志賀城的城主。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:44.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什麼時候 我比父親的歲數還大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有一個人沒死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒做啊 什麼都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:02.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,睡那些女人的事情 我沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:06.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他如此堅持說什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:09.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把他殺掉的話 我們就會變得和那些傢伙一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個可憐的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:17.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾米·乳 讓他揉揉你的胸部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼不被射死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把屍體的首級切下來拿去祭奠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:24.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然可恨 但死了以後便成佛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,身體就用來造火藥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:33.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們漂流者的傳聞轉眼間就傳到了周邊的村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:37.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者幫助了精靈族的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,襲擊了地方官的駐地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:44.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 當被困在地方官城堡裡的女精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:46.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都回到了各自的村莊之時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:50.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,令人困惑的傳聞轉變為了讓大家歡呼雀躍的確信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那些回到各個村莊的女精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:58.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,同時也帶回了信長所給的精心準備的土特產
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:01.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,檄文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,檄文的內容真的很有信長的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:08.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是份可以安撫掌控讀者心情的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想要國家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:13.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,來加入我們的隊列吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:18.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要再次把你們的女人交出去麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:23.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還要讓她們被下一任的地方官當成慰安婦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:29.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 他在附件上說明奧爾特帝國已經危在旦夕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:33.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,通過展示在城裡找到的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是多麼狡猾的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:41.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後精靈族們陸續回應起義
