Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.10,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(818.4,697.8)}織田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:17.86,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz21.55\pos(1063.2,760.2)}豐久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:17.86,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz21.55\pos(916.8,469.8)}島津
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:22.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:25.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這又怎樣啊 紫那傢伙
