Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:28.99,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(1329.6,1057.5,1254,669,0,3500)}請勿打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:29.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 什麼 什麼漂流者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.62,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1579.2,275.1)}奧爾特帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:34.62,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1507.2,348)}帝都威爾利那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:38.13,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1507.2,219.9)}大治藩公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:38.13,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1430.4,279.9)}聖日爾曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:38.13,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1356,159.9)}館宮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:41.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,無論在東還是在西都打了敗仗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,並且在北方有迷之軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:47.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上精靈族的叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:51.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,算起來 這個國家也是要完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.39,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1572,272.7)}奧爾特帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.39,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1490.4,448.8)}帝都威爾利那 貴族院
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 戰局一直在變差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說 士兵不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:01.11,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1636.8,270.3)}總作戰會議
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:01.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我國四十年間一直都在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:05.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就連後方的駐紮兵都派出去打仗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,物資也是完全不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:11.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本土和附屬地區的稅收和掠奪也快接近極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是應該考慮講和了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼傻話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:18.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是國父大人所想的萬年帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是這個國家的國策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:23.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能如此簡單就摒棄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:30.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好 大家好 遲到了 抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:32.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓你們久等了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:33.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,挺久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,聖日爾曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:41.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,遲到了 遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:43.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,出來的時候被各種事情耽誤了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:46.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那一群人妖是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,噓 你說得太大聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被聽到的話可不知道會被做什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:54.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是聖日耳曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:56.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有帝國的四分之一的巨大貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他是在國父建國之時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第一位倒戈投靠國父的貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,傳聞如果沒有伯爵的叛變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾特帝國也不可能建成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,從那以後再也沒有人敢對他提出任何意見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不需要親自上戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:18.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只是隨心所欲地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:23.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,幫助了國父…這不是五十年前的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:23.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:27.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人妖到底多少歲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:30.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為我的遲到道歉 我給你們帶來了個好消息喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可不要被嚇到了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:38.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有往西方戰場上運送物資的一些貨船隊麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:42.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們 有沒有什麼可以拿來寫字的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,寫字的東西 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:47.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下 請用我這隻口紅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:50.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 請用我這隻口紅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴 快點給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:57.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說過無數次這條運輸路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:59.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不太行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:05.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在被發現 然後完全淪陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:09.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,又被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 那樣根本救不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,又有一艘船被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:16.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩下幾艘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:17.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:19.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 這幫「商人」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這幫古彬連商業聯合的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.96,Drifters Normal JL,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1509.6,553.5)}古彬連聯合商會 夏依洛克商店艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:34.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,夏依洛克商會獅鷲快遞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:36.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:42.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾特的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:47.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,古彬連特產的魚獸油脂的滋味如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,給我吃飽喝足吧混賬傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:53.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後拿去當慰問你們小鬍子國父的特產吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:55.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圖拉圖拉圖拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:59.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 那個「圖拉圖拉圖拉」是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是提督教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:06.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,突襲成功後就這樣喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:08.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圖拉圖拉圖拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:11.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圖拉圖拉圖拉圖拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:22.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這次也贏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:35.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,四面八方都吹起了戰鬥的號角呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:41.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不應該把東方的聯合商會當成敵人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後殖民地發生了叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:51.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,精靈族的殖民地貌似已經高舉了叛亂的旗幟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:55.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 精靈族 真可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:58.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要管他們 只不過是一些農奴的暴動而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:01.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}更應該重視西方的戰況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:03.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:08.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾特帝國是單方面往周圍擴張的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:12.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了叛亂就代表著不僅僅是精靈族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:16.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而是所有的殖民地的不滿一起地爆發出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:18.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就會像止不住的野火一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:22.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,各處殖民地將像開慶典一樣爆發超大型的叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:27.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後叛亂位於向西進軍的必經之路上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:31.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,處於西方的國家主力軍隊就會與本國相隔絕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:34.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊討厭 這個國家不是已經完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:39.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我忽然想起了些急事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:43.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先回去了 大家繼續加油戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:44.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下 怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:51.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了 這樣下去不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:54.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,順便把那個燭臺順回去吧 那張畫也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:57.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻聯繫精靈族的叛亂軍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 聽說漂流者也參與其中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:02.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那我親自去接觸他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是精靈族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}也請帶上我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:16.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:21.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是菲佐納村的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:22.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是夏拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:26.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟看了那樣的信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是精靈族就應該站出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:31.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的村莊也有人不斷地加入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:32.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下來一定能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:34.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,挑起這一切的漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都是些怎樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你問我他們是怎樣的人 我也不好答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:41.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能說都是些怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:44.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,無論這些漂流者怎麼樣幫助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都不是精靈族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:48.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些短耳朵的人類對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠信任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可以信任 至少我是這樣認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你還在生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:02.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,該消氣了吧 老大不小了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是曾經的右大臣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:07.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,歸根結底 你為什麼這麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不是明擺著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:11.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼要搞成村長們的合議制啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:13.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這下全都化整為零了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本來你還能成為國王的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:19.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不懂什麼策略
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:22.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不懂別人的腦袋裡在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:28.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信 你能完全看透別人的腦袋都在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:32.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你卻看不透別人心中所想之事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:35.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的精靈族一定會跟著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,國王之類的什麼都能當
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:41.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 總有一天會把箭頭指向我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在不知道哪個寺廟裡睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:46.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,醒來的時候已經被火箭所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:50.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想要在這裡重蹈本能寺的覆轍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:55.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你說你能看清人的內心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:57.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是站著說話不腰疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:59.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:02.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,謀反的滋味我已經嘗夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:04.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你真經常被別人背叛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟信勝兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:10.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,勝家和林 淺井 松永兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:13.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,荒木 波多野 別所 光秀還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:14.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:18.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我決定了的事就一定會去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓你成為王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:26.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:27.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把廁所的泥土…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:30.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:35.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心翼翼地幹哦 不然會被炸飛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:38.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,夏拉 你去告訴其他村的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:42.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把廁所和豬圈附近的泥土都搬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:45.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是有多喜歡糞便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,信先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我去問了各個村的工匠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:53.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然這個東西太難製造了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:59.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK}堺和國友的那群傢伙還真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:02.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,誰可以製作出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 擅長鐵器的矮人族可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:09.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他們都比較擅長這方面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:13.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「矮人族」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:19.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是教導你們精靈族箭術的教官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那須資隆与一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,別磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:27.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要讓不成氣候的你們進行最嚴格的鍛煉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:30.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們求生不得求死不能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:34.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在說話的前後都給我加上「源氏萬歲」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:36.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,源氏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:37.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,來進行不僅是百發百中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:43.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而是以百發萬中為目標的猛烈特訓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的 源氏萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:50.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他說話雖然像是開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:53.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但認真起來可是又完美又可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:55.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一可惜的地方就是短耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:59.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:02.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那須兄弟十一人之中最小的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:05.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而我又是家族之中最笨挫的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:08.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,說起哥哥們的美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:11.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是踏在地上就會有鮮花盛開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:12.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大海被劈開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黃金從天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:18.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有這種程度都不足掛齒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對是騙人的源氏萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:32.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是薩州的刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:34.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有東西都傾注於這一擊之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要考慮這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:37.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:41.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那一擊砍偏了或者被躲開了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,乾淨俐落地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:46.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黃泉上的先人 都會稱讚你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:50.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,精靈族的人不可能學會我的刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:53.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼想都不適合他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:56.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,弓箭倒是很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:59.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似全部人都是射箭的天才一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我和村裡的工匠…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:07.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這種躁動不安的感覺到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼要到來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:14.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這種感覺 不像是奧爾特的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:18.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼要到來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:22.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,和關原有著同樣的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:24.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人反胃的戰爭的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找 把他們找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:35.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 吉爾德萊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:39.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這臭味 是漂流者的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:45.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,殺掉 把漂流者都殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:48.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要在無花果結果之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:51.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓它枯萎殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:22:03.31,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Blaze your way 暁の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:22:03.31,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开拓你的道路 向着拂晓之空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:07.56,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Bloodthirsty Noble Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:07.56,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚战士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:12.57,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滾る心に刃と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:12.57,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}灼热翻腾的心中之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:19.66,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}無に成る大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:19.66,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高举心无旁骛的大义之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:31.13,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}陽炎は揺れるシンフォニー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:31.13,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}热浪就如晃荡的交响乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:41.14,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}その声　響く三日月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.34,0:22:41.14,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那歌声 在新月之夜下荡漾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:44.48,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}こんなにくべる炎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.35,0:22:44.48,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如此久久不息的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:46.98,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明けぬ夜は無いと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:46.98,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不存在永不破晓的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:50.98,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}生を叫ぶ衝動 輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:50.98,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}呼喊生存的冲动 闪耀着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:56.15,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Blaze your way 暁の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:56.15,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开拓你的道路 向着拂晓之空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:23:00.45,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Bloodthirsty Noble Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:23:00.45,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚战士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:05.21,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滲む痛み引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.53,0:23:05.21,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}与被染红的痛楚一同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:12.30,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}果てない今日を踏んだ大地へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:12.30,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}冲破无尽的今日 迈向新大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:19.51,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}栄光を歌う peace at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:19.51,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}歌颂荣光 终归和平
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:23.64,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}更なる大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:23.64,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高举更为雄壮的大义之旗
